# Battery SOC Estimation using Coulomb Counting

This project focuses on estimating the State of Charge (SOC) of a battery using the Coulomb counting method.

## Key Concepts:
- State of Charge (SOC)
- Coulomb counting method
- Battery charge/discharge behavior

## Methodology:
- Assumed initial SOC
- Applied constant current
- Calculated SOC variation over time
- Plotted SOC vs Time graph

## Tools Used:
- MATLAB

## Output:
- Graph: SOC (%) vs Time

## Applications:
- Battery monitoring systems (BMS)
- Electric vehicle energy management
